{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "a1b2c3d4-e5f6-7890-abcd-ondemand-service",
    "name": "OnDemand Service API",
    "description": "REST collection for the Spring Boot OnDemand Service (`com.runalb.ondemand_service`).\n\n**Auth** (`/api/v1/auth/**`): login + OTP + refresh + logout routes are public (no Bearer).\n\n**Users** (`/api/v1/users`): signup (`POST`) is public. Other user routes require Bearer and user ownership.\n\n**Portal / Merchants** (`/api/v1/portal/merchants/**`): Bearer required; ownership checks enforced via `AuthService.assertAuthenticatedUserOwnsMerchant`.\n\n**Business** (`/api/v1/business/**`): Bearer required. Currently only `POST /api/v1/business` is implemented; list/get/update/delete handlers return `501 Not Implemented`.\n\n**Catalog** (`/api/v1/catalog/**`): `GET` requires authentication; non-GET endpoints require `ROLE_SUPER_ADMIN`.\n\n**Integration + Webhook note**: security/filter rules exist for `/api/v1/integration/**` and `/webhook/**`, but no corresponding controllers are currently present in this project module.\n\nDefault `baseUrl`: `http://localhost:8080`. Set `{{apiKey}}` after merchant creation if/when integration controllers are available.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl", "value": "http://localhost:8080" },
    { "key": "emailId", "value": "hello@runalb.com" },
    { "key": "password", "value": "runal@123" },
    { "key": "accessToken", "value": "" },
    { "key": "refreshToken", "value": "" },
    { "key": "merchantId", "value": "1" },
    { "key": "userId", "value": "1" },
    { "key": "businessId", "value": "1" },
    { "key": "configId", "value": "1" },
    { "key": "categoryId", "value": "1" },
    { "key": "serviceId", "value": "1" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "description": "`auth.controller.AuthController` — public routes; no Bearer.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Login (email + password)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{emailId}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{password}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/login",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "login"]
            },
            "description": "`AuthLoginRequest` → `AuthLoginResponse`. Copy `accessToken` / `refreshToken` into collection variables."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Login email — request OTP",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"user@example.com\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/login/email/request-otp",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "login", "email", "request-otp"]
            },
            "description": "`AuthEmailOtpRequest`. In dev, OTP may be logged server-side."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Login email — verify OTP",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"user@example.com\",\n  \"otp\": \"123456\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/login/email/verify-otp",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "login", "email", "verify-otp"]
            },
            "description": "`AuthEmailVerifyOtpRequest` — returns `AuthLoginResponse`."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Forgot password — request OTP",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"user@example.com\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/forgot-password/email/request-otp",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "forgot-password", "email", "request-otp"]
            },
            "description": "`AuthEmailOtpRequest` — returns `AuthOtpRequestResponse`."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Forgot password — reset with OTP",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"user@example.com\",\n  \"otp\": \"123456\",\n  \"newPassword\": \"newPassword123\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/forgot-password/email/reset-password",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "forgot-password", "email", "reset-password"]
            },
            "description": "`AuthForgotPasswordResetRequest` — 204 No Content."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Login mobile — request OTP",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"mobileNumber\": \"+14155552671\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/login/mobile/request-otp",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "login", "mobile", "request-otp"]
            },
            "description": "`AuthMobileOtpRequest` (E.164)."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Login mobile — verify OTP",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"mobileNumber\": \"+14155552671\",\n  \"otp\": \"123456\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/login/mobile/verify-otp",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "login", "mobile", "verify-otp"]
            },
            "description": "`AuthMobileVerifyOtpRequest` — returns `AuthLoginResponse`."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Refresh token",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"refreshToken\": \"{{refreshToken}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/refresh-token",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "refresh-token"]
            },
            "description": "`AuthRefreshRequest` — returns new `AuthLoginResponse`."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Logout",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"refreshToken\": \"{{refreshToken}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/logout",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "logout"]
            },
            "description": "`AuthLogoutRequest` — 204 No Content."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Users",
      "description": "`user.controller.UserController` — `/api/v1/users`. `POST` is public; other routes require Bearer and ownership of `userId`.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Create user (signup)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"newuser@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"password123\",\n  \"name\": \"New User\",\n  \"mobileNumber\": \"+14155552671\",\n  \"roles\": [\"CUSTOMER\"]\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "users"]
            },
            "description": "`UserCreateRequest` — required non-empty `roles` (`RoleNameEnum`: CUSTOMER, PROVIDER, ADMIN, SUPER_ADMIN); each must exist in DB. `mobileNumber` optional (E.164 if set). 201 + `UserResponse`."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Get user",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/{{userId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "users", "{{userId}}"]
            },
            "description": "`AuthService.assertAuthenticatedUserOwnsUserId` — principal must match `userId`."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Patch user",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Updated Name\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/{{userId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "users", "{{userId}}"]
            },
            "description": "`UserUpdateRequest` — partial update; self-only."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Delete user (deactivate)",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/{{userId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "users", "{{userId}}"]
            },
            "description": "204 No Content — `UserService.deactivateUser`."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Reactivate user",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/{{userId}}/reactivate",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "users", "{{userId}}", "reactivate"]
            },
            "description": "Self-only — returns `UserResponse`."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
